Harmoney Biography


Harmoney was born and raised in Brooklyn, NY. Influenced by singer/songwriters like Jamie Foxx, 

Tank, Ginuwine and Missy Elliott, Harmoney knew he had found something in music that he loved more 

than anything else. Creating his own music became his strongest emotional outlet.

Harmoney focuses on deeper lyrical content expressing feelings many are afraid to say. His honesty 

and soothing intonation tug at the heartstrings of the ladies. Harmoneyâ€™s subject matter ranges 

from the streets to the bedroom catering to his male counterparts as well as his female followers.

Harmoney is currently a singer/songwriter signed to 4Ever Young Music Group. He is a full time 

recording artist and a skilled songwriter. His sultry voice and heart-felt words have afforded him 

the opportunity to be the next heavily sought after Alternative R&B/ Hip-Hop/R&B sensation to hit 

the airwaves.


By: Ambre Tomlinson
